How to connect created instance with Terminal is steps under below

first connect instance in aws ------->which means launch instance normally----->select instance -----> connect select option here 

open first terminal----->cd Downloads/--------> select created instance ------->select connect------> in connect select option here as -------> select SSH client
------>copy and paste 3rd on terminal--------> again copy and paste example command on terminal---------> yes------> over

